    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small, spherical stone fruits; pulpy drupes of certain species; or a sub-genus of Prunus (family Rosaceæ). The color of the flesh may vary from yellow and red to almost purple-red.</Note_Text>
